{"tid":2262814,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（皇仁的損失）皇仁舊生會暫停何君堯會籍兩年","createTime":"2020-10-29T11:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T11:54:04.000Z","uid":41343,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5cdb8cd29688ecfce3b4c35d7b61d81f995ef45f","tid":2262814,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T11:17:06.000Z","msg":"《立場新聞》獲悉，立法會議員何君堯被母校皇仁書院的舊生會暫停會籍，為期兩年至 2022 年。何君堯本身是皇仁舊生會的永久會員，消息指，如果他希望恢復會籍，需要在 2022 年後重新申請入會。何君堯在去年 7.21 事件中被拍攝到向「白衣人」舉拇指讚好，引發皇仁舊生會會員不滿，去年底舊生會曾作問卷諮詢，高達 83% 受訪會員贊同終止何君堯會籍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%9A%87%E4%BB%81%E8%88%8A%E7%94%9F%E6%9C%83%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E6%9C%83%E7%B1%8D-%E7%82%BA%E6%9C%9F%E5%85%A9%E5%B9%B4%E8%87%B3-2022-%E5%B9%B4-%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E6%9C%83%E7%B1%8D%E9%9C%80%E9%87%8D%E6%96%B0%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259A%2587%25E4%25BB%2581%25E8%2588%258A%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25B1%258D-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2587%25B3-2022-%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E6%2581%25A2%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25B1%258D%25E9%259C%2580%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kijv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=8305caac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%259A%2587%25E4%25BB%2581%25E8%2588%258A%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259A%25AB%25E5%2581%259C%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25A0%25AF%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25B1%258D-%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%2587%25B3-2022-%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E6%2581%25A2%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25B1%258D%25E9%259C%2580%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%2F&h=ebb5939b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.t